entry.title: KALTCHUK/Z80_Modular_Computer
entry.summary: "Anyone who has brought up CP/M on a homebuilt computer has felt this moment of elation. A myriad of connections are properly closed; bits are flying at lightning speeds over busses and through circuits and program logic, to produce a single prompt". Gary Kildall
